    "This was done following recent work that showed that answer matching had perfect agreement with human ratings [18].",
    "Prompt: Autorater for answer matchingYou are an impartial judge.",
    "Your task is to evaluate whether the candidate answer is correct compared to the gold answer.You must output only 'True' or 'False'.",
